F. R. HINMAN et al. v. UNITED AIRPORTS COMPANY OF CALIFORNIA, Limited. No. 9575. Circuit Court oí Appeals, Ninth Circuit. July 29, 1940. Murchison & Clopton, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellants. Newlin & Ashburn, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, MATHEWS, and HEALY, Circuit Judges,

*938PER CURIAM.

On stipulation of counsel for respective parties, and good cause therefor appearing, ordered appeal herein dismissed, that a decree of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and mandate of this court issued forthwith.
